Package ch.psi.wica.controlsystem.epics

Enum EpicsChannelType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EpicsChannelType>
      • ch.psi.wica.controlsystem.epics.EpicsChannelType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<EpicsChannelType>
    public enum EpicsChannelType
extends Enum<EpicsChannelType>
    Represents the type of an EPICS Channel. This can potentially change every time new channel metadata is received.
    Implementation Note:
    The support here is premised on the use of Wica with the PSI CA channel access client library.
